      <li>
        <strong>Empathetic Objection Handling:</strong>
        <ul>
          <li><b>‚ÄúIs it safe & effective?‚Äù</b> ‚Üí Show trials/FDA evidence; offer peer contacts.</li>
          <li><b>‚ÄúIt‚Äôs too expensive.‚Äù</b> ‚Üí Frame as investment, ROI, insurance reimbursement options, flexible financing.</li>
          <li><b>‚ÄúToo complex for
